 (6, 1, '2018-11-27 09:17:28', '2018-11-27 09:17:28', '<h1>\n					SERVICES & OFFERINGS\n				</h1>\n			<h2>It\'s time to  start your adventure with JKN Solutions</h2>		\n		<p>The modelling of the system is set that it can be accessed via the internet directly; through web browsers or mobile applications as a service to be used and implemented, rather than just a software to simply use. Subscribers can pay for higher tier services and use the web or mobile application at their leisure.​</p>		\n										<img width="1024" height="512" src="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cellphone-1024x512.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cellphone-1024x512.jpg 1024w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cellphone-300x150.jpg 300w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cellphone-768x384.jpg 768w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cellphone-1536x768.jpg 1536w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cellphone.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />											\n			<h5>REAL TIME INTERACTION</h5><p>Streaming and live chat </p>		\n										<img width="800" height="417" src="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cloud10.png" alt="" srcset="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cloud10.png 800w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cloud10-300x156.png 300w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cloud10-768x400.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" />											\n			<h5>Customize your own Environment</h5><p>Choose what you want to do!</p>		\n										<img width="300" height="168" src="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dataan.jpg" alt="" />											\n			<h5>MARKETING TOOLS</h5><p>Works on all devices. Social media connectivity.</p>		\n										<img width="702" height="336" src="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dataanalytics.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dataanalytics.jpg 702w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dataanalytics-300x144.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px" />											\n			<h5>DATA ANALYTICS</h5><p>Understand your audience and reach. See sit usage details.</p>		\n			<h4>Service PROVIDER</h4>		\n		<p>Clients: Ability to post feedback/trouble reports &amp; Ability to directly message service provider to ask questions​</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Ability to customize environment-dependent on the package chosen\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Access to marketing tools\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Post content, Email and live chat with customers\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Facebook, Instagram ads​\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width="1024" height="576" src="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/buistiers-1024x576.png" alt="" srcset="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/buistiers-1024x576.png 1024w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/buistiers-300x169.png 300w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/buistiers-768x432.png 768w, http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/buistiers.png 1174w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />											\n			<h4>NEWS DISTRIBUTOR</h4>		\n		<p>Subscribers: Ability to join a live stream (view a live stream)​ &amp; Ability to post related new stories/alerts​</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Ability to customize environment\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Ability to live stream stories or events​\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Post Stories & Archive stories/events​\n									</li>\n								<li >\n										Access to marketing tools\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width="1024" height="575" src="http://www.jknsolutions.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/news-tiers-1024x575.png"